<header>
  <h5>Select Your Goal</h5>
</header>

<div class="goal-wrapper">
  <div class="goal-block money" data-route="traffic">
    <i class="large-icon icon-money"></i>
    <h6>Promote a Sale/Discount</h6>

    <p>Point visitors to your latest deal, bargain, or giveaway.</p>
    <button class="button" {{action 'selectGoal' 'interstitial.traffic'}}>Select This Goal</button>
  </div>

  <div class="goal-block call" data-route="call">
    <i class="large-icon icon-call"></i>
    <h6>Talk to Your Visitors</h6>

    <p>Encourage mobile visitors to give you a ring.</p>
    <button class="button" {{action 'selectGoal' 'interstitial.call'}}>Select This Goal</button>
  </div>

  <div class="goal-block contacts" data-route="email">
    <i class="large-icon icon-contacts"></i>
    <h6>Grow Your Mailing List</h6>

    <p>Convert one-time visits into lasting connections.</p>
    <button class="button" {{action 'selectGoal' 'interstitial.email'}}>Select This Goal</button>
  </div>

  <div class="goal-block facebook" data-route="social">
    <i class="large-icon icon-thumbsup"></i>
    <h6>Get Facebook Likes</h6>

    <p>Expand your social reach to maximize word of mouth.</p>
    <button class="button" {{action 'selectGoal' 'interstitial.social'}}>Select This Goal</button>
  </div>

  <div class="goal-block other" data-route="other">
    <i class="large-icon icon-other"></i>
    <h6>Other</h6>

    <p>Don't see your goal? Customize Hello Bar to fit your needs.</p>
    <button class="button" {{action 'selectGoal' 'goals'}}>Select This Goal</button>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>Select one of the goals above. You can always change this later.</p>

  <div>
    <a href="/">I'll create it later - take me back</a>
  </div>

  {{interstitial/helpers/i-need-help model=model}}

  <p>
    <small>
      <a href="/users/sign_out" data-method="delete" class="deemphasize">Sign Out</a>
    </small>
  </p>
</footer>
